crescent mezzanine fund vi closes on more than  billion  business wire crescent mezzanine fund vi closes on more than  billion august    am eastern daylight time los angelesbusiness wirecrescent capital group lp a leading investment firm focused on below investment grade credit announces the successful close of crescent mezzanine partners vi “fund vi” investors committed more than  billion to fund vi meaningfully exceeding the initial fundraising target of  billion and representing the largest private mezzanine offering in crescent mezzanine’s history “we are particularly grateful to the significant number of existing limited partners that chose to participate in this fund” said jeanmarc chapus managing partner and cofounder of crescent capital group “we are also pleased to welcome the support of a number of new investors in fund vi we believe that our experience investing and sourcing in excess of  billion of capital in over  mezzanine transactions on behalf of our funds and coinvestors for over  years was a key element to our success” the crescent mezzanine group is a leading source of mezzanine capital providing private equity sponsors and management teams with longterm financing to complete leveraged buyouts acquisitions recapitalizations and laterstage growth financings the group targets investments in companies that are typically controlled by private equity sponsors and have enterprise values in excess of  million about crescent capital crescent capital group lp an secregistered investment adviser is headquartered in los angeles with offices in boston london and new york with approximately  investment professionals the firm invests at all levels of the capital structure with a significant focus on below investment grade credit through strategies that invest in senior bank loans high yield debt mezzanine debt distressed debt and other private debt securities as of june   crescent capital group manages approximately  billion in assets with a relatively equal split between marketable securities and proprietary closedend private investment partnerships contacts mediamendel communications llcbill mendel  billmendelcommunicationscom contacts mediamendel communications llcbill mendel  billmendelcommunicationscom search advanced news search advanced news search log in sign up home loginposition position position position position  the relevance of partnership the virtue of patience the importance of teamwork the value of listening the advantage of experience mezzanine loginmezzanine   judgment honed over two decades of investment experience the value of experiencecrescent’s mezzanine strategy is one of the leading independent global providers of mezzanine capital since  crescents mezzanine strategy has developed a reputation as a reliable provider of junior debt capital primarily to fund shareholder transitions on behalf of private equity firms we believe our reputation is a result of our extensive investment experience broad transaction sourcing capabilities and disciplined investment approach our objective is to provide investors with substantial current income and capital appreciation by investing in a diversified portfolio of mezzanine securities investments generally take the form of private debt securities with equity participation in connection with buyouts recapitalizations and refinancings   investors committed more than  billion to crescent mezzanine partners vii “fund vii” exceeding the initial fundraising target of  billion and representing the largest private mezzanine offering in crescent mezzanine’s history our experience investing in over  mezzanine transactions for  years is a key element to our continued successproviding financing to private equity sponsors jeanmarc chapus managing partner and cofounder of crescent capital group crescent mezzanine a message from jeanmarc chapus chris wright and tyrone chang  watch video crescent mezzanine a message from jeanmarc chapus chris wright and tyrone chang   bizapedia