ition our easy to install modular mezzanine design easily bolts together to allow for rapid installation future expansion or even relocation freespace mezzanines™ aren’t just for storage our rigid frame design is perfect for metal buildings conveyor support equipment platforms inplant offices manufacturing activities walkways or stair tower whatever you may need to support above floor level fcp can create the right structure plus with our design and use of lightweight hightensile materials we are able to install the new structure over existing equipment or stored items with a minimum of support columns thereby maximizing the usable floor space under the mezzanine fcp freespace mezzanines™ are designed to comply with all applicable building codes ubc cbc and ibc as well as meeting the rigorous specifications demanded in seismically active zones codes  specs fcp freespace mezzanine™ utilizes structural square tube columns to save space while creating superior rigidity all components are designed to facilitate ease of installation the hightensile steel framing members and our rigid frame momentconnections allow greater spans and the ability to meet seismic zone  requirements  framing systems are designed to meet or exceed local california and international building code standards all fcp freespace mezzanines tm follow the guidelines of the applicable code agencies ansi aisc asce ubc cbc boca sbc ada and osha free space mezzaninesequipment platforms office platforms observation towers conveyor platforms catwalks solar equipment platforms  home site map request for proposal the choice of industry leadersrfpfcpmezzaninecom call today   equipment platforms equipment platforms lwolfe fcp designs custom support platforms for a wide variety of unique applications no matter the size and shape of your particular equipment fcp can design the right equipment platforms to support it from entertainment and defense to manufacturing and retail fcp has the experience to design a system that’s just right for your needs to maximize useable floor space our equipment support platforms are designed to fit around any existing obstructions and can accommodate stairways and access locations as needed our system designers will create industrial structures to meet your specific load and conveyor platform requirements whether it is for storage material handling equipment or concentrated loads of heavy equipment the unique design of fcp freespace mezzanines ™ also allows for fast installation future expansion and can be dismantled and reassembled if required we’ve even designed support platforms with rollers and air jacks support platformscustom metal buildings multistory metal buildings canopies pump and equipment buildings blue sky homes